_sText:
This is a quite popular zombie hunting map I made.
It contains doors that can be used by CTs only to seal certain areas.
There is a button in the control room that opens all doors (zombies want to reach that button).
The FPS are excellent and so is the gameplay, thanks to the Elite Hunterz team on whose server I could test the map and finally create this version!
Recommended for limited ammo and zombies that are about as fast as humans.
Features:
 + custom radar overview and radio areas
 + excellent FPS and gameplay
 + enough space for 64 players to camp and hunt
 + CT-only doors and a secret weapon
